32-5A-5. Schedule of rates.

The per vehicle wheel rate imposed pursuant to §32-5A-1 may be imposed according to the manufacturer's shipping weight, including accessories, and may vary according to the following schedule:

(1)Two thousand pounds or less, inclusive;

(2)From 2001 to 4000 pounds, inclusive;

(3)From 4001 to 6000 pounds, inclusive;

(4)Over 6000 pounds.

Source:SL 1994, ch 244, §2.
